org.interledger.psk

クラス PskEncryptionHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.interledger.psk.PskMessage.Header
      • org.interledger.psk.PskEncryptionHeader

  • public class PskEncryptionHeader
extends PskMessage.Header
    Convenience header representing the public Encryption header found in PSK messages.

      • aesGcm

        public static PskEncryptionHeader aesGcm(byte[] authenticationTag)
        Constructs an instance of the header with the AES-GCM encryption type and provided authentication tag value.
        パラメータ:
        authenticationTag - The authentication tag value. May be null.
        戻り値:
        A PskEncryptionHeader instance based on the authentication tag if present.

      • fromHeader

        public static PskEncryptionHeader fromHeader(PskMessage.Header header)
        Constructs an instance of the header of an existing header with the appropriate values.
        パラメータ:
        header - An existing header
        戻り値:
        An encryption header
        例外:
        RuntimeException - if an encryption header can't be constructed of the given header
